#

Caprese Salad with Fresh Mozzarella

10 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

SaladAppetizerQuick

Description

A refreshing and vibrant salad with juicy tomatoes, creamy mozzarella, and aromatic basil, drizzled with a hint of balsamic for a delightful taste.

Ingredients

  • fresh mozzarella: 8 oz
  • ripe tomatoes: 4 medium
  • fresh basil leaves: 1 cup
  • balsamic glaze: 2 tbsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
